'''Bergþórshvoll''' (usually Anglicized as ''Bergthorsknoll'') is an important setting in the [[Icelandic saga]] ''[[Njál's saga]]'', the home and scene of the final [[Execution by burning|burning]] of [[Njáll Þorgeirsson]] and his entire family.

