[[File:Baeretswil Weissenbachbruecke DVZO.jpg|thumb|right|A steam train of the DVZO crosses the Weissenbachbrücke in Bäretswil]]
[[File:Bahnhof Uster mit zwei Lok-Remisen 2011-08-07 14-47-42 ShiftN.jpg|thumb|right|The ''lok remise'' at Uster]]
The '''Dampfbahn-Verein Zürcher Oberland''' (DVZO) is a [[heritage railway]] association based in the [[Switzerland|Swiss]] [[canton of Zurich]]. The association preserves various items of [[rolling stock]], utilising the historic ''lok remise'' or [[Motive power depot|engine shed]] at [[Uster railway station|Uster station]], and also operates the preserved railway between [[Hinwil railway station|Hinwil]] and [[Bauma railway station|Bauma]] stations over a section of the former [[Uerikon–Bauma railway|Uerikon to Bauma railway]] (UeBB).<ref name=lokrem>{{cite web | url = http://www.dvzo.ch/?N1_ID=190&N2_ID=212&Language=de | title = Uster: Die älteste Lok- und Wagenremise der Schweiz | language = German |trans-title=Uster: The oldest locomotive and carriage house in Switzerland | publisher = DVZO | accessdate = 2013-04-03}}</ref><ref name=saw12-13>{{cite book | title = Eisenbahnatlas Schweiz | year = 2012 | publisher = Verlag Schweers + Wall GmbH | isbn=978-3-89494-130-7 | pages = 12–13}}</ref>

