'''''Fighting Spiders''''' is a [[drama]] [[television program]] from [[Singapore]] that premiered on [[MediaCorp Channel 5]] on April 14, 2009. The show was created by [[Ngin Chiang Meng]] and Jenny Lim.<ref name=MediaCorp>{{cite web|title=Fighting Spiders 斗蜘蛛|url=http://www4.mediacorp.sg/contentdistribution/programme/detail.php?prog_id=360|publisher=Media Corp|accessdate=17 September 2013}}</ref>
==Plot== ''Fighting Spiders'' is the story of three boys in the 1960s — Soon Lee (Edwin Goh), Charlie (Liang Shijie Jason) and Peter (Frederick Fielding) — and their adventure to find the legendary King Spider.
