Ethnic '''[[Georgians]] in [[Greece]]''' number around 27,400.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.statistics.gr/portal/page/portal/ESYE/BUCKET/General/nws_SAM01_EN.PDF |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2014-06-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131225192921/http://www.statistics.gr/portal/page/portal/ESYE/BUCKET/General/nws_SAM01_EN.PDF |archivedate=2013-12-25 |df= }}</ref><ref>[http://diaspora.gov.ge/?p=2503 ქართველები საბერძნეთში] [[State Ministry on Diaspora Issues of Georgia]]</ref> Most of them reside in [[Athens]], [[Thessaloniki]] and the island of [[Crete]]. As Greeks, Georgians also practice [[Eastern Orthodoxy]].

